node.text:
Don’t get stranded this holiday weekend without the SelvaRey Cadillac Mojito. #SelvaReyRum #TropicalLuxury⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Cadillac Mojito 
1 1/2 oz SelvaRey White Rum⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
1 oz Fresh Lime Juice⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
2 tsp Superfine Sugar⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
10 Mint Leaves⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Splash of Club Soda⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Muddle mint, lime, and sugar in a glass⁣⁣. Add rum, ice, and stir. Top with club soda⁣⁣. Garnish with a mint sprig.
